### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@userId = YOUR_USER_ID_HERE
@accountId = YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID_HERE

### List Accounts (requires X-User-Id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounts
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Create Savings Pocket
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounts/pockets
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "type": "SAVINGS"
}

### Create School Fees Pocket
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounts/pockets
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "type": "SCHOOL_FEES"
}

### Get Account Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounts/{{accountId}}/balance
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Get Account Balance (without auth - should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/accounts/{{accountId}}/balance
